{{Top|leg}}
The '''Trade Hall''' in [[Cormond]] was the center of [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal's]] commercial interests. Meetings and policy making took place within its halls, and the shipping carried on throughout the rest of Brentaal was directed from within its walls.<ref name="Into the Core Worlds">{{JournalCite|7|Into the Core Worlds}}</ref>

The Trade Hall held several expansive trade floors, thousands of offices, gardens, and shopping centers. It also had a private [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]], which, while permits to land there cost more, was a mark of prestige for all who did.<ref name="Into the Core Worlds" />

